Subject: [PATCH] netfilter: nftables: avoid overflows in nft_hash_buckets()
Patch-mainline: v5.13-rc1
Git-commit: a54754ec9891830ba548e2010c889e3c8146e449
References: CVE-2021-47013 bsc#1220641 CVE-2021-46992 bsc#1220638

Number of buckets being stored in 32bit variables, we have to
ensure that no overflows occur in nft_hash_buckets()

